Package com.gcu.agms.model.gate

Class AssignmentModel

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.agms.model.gate.AssignmentModel
public class AssignmentModel extends Object
Represents a gate assignment in the Airport Gate Management System. This model connects flights with gates for specific time periods and tracks the status of each assignment.
